des: This skill enables users to effortlessly track their Aramex shipments in real-time using simple voice commands. Whether you're waiting for a package or need to check the status of a delivery, this skill provides a convenient and hands-free way to stay updated.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
